The Blitz turn order card is included in the Buried Secrets expansion (BS158)
Use the Blitz turn order card if you want to increase the difficulty of the nemesis.
{newline}
Setup:
Replace a nemesis turn order card in the turn order deck with the Blitz turn order card.
{newline}
Rules:
When the Blitz turn order card is drawn, resolve the nemesis main phase once. Then, resolve the nemesis turn as usual.
The Blitz turn order card counds as a nemesis turn order card.
